@* PSEUDOCODE PLAN
1. Extract greeting/introduction block from first column.
2. Place greeting block in its own full-width row (col-12) above main grid.
3. Keep second row as three columns (col-12 col-md-4) for original column content minus greeting.
4. Column 1 now only holds About card.
5. Columns 2 and 3 remain unchanged.
